Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮堂光、龙咲海和凤凰寺风三人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被艾美诺公主召唤成为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救异世界锡菲罗的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是个由神官谢加图支配
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔物蠢动的恐怖世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先由我来!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光等人和救命恩人菲力欧分手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找名为艾斯古托的矿物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,急忙前去传说之泉艾蒂露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,固执的魔操士爱尔希欧蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走得那么快…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿先生究竟要去到哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了!已经穿过沉默之森了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经能使用魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞呀!飞呀!\N飞到艾蒂露娜去!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来!飞来!\N飞来!艾蒂露娜!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 如果没经古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传授使用魔法的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀 我也未曾学习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但古列夫已经被敌人杀死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我以后\N毫无魔法地战斗吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题啊 小海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我能用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是魔物啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!把小风小海还给我!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风!小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光…小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上救你们出来!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风!小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好辛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了!太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢你 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我能用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能打倒那种魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我…\N明白洗涤物的感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的是什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.19,0:06:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能又是魔物!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说笑吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何那么不停出现啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样 身体支持不住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿!原来你没事!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要以莫歌拿先生为榜样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快去艾蒂露娜之泉吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赞成!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个很荒凉的村落呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[难道]?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫说过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗因为神官谢加图
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成一个魔物徘徊的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个村…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是什么呀!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可能跌进陷阱了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是[可能]!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这次明白 的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来有人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大…大家好!\N我们不是坏人!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不是那样说\N就会明白的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情形的确有古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可用那么\N危险的东西指着人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摆起姿势了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!别开玩笑啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候祸不单行…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!用魔法!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脚!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么!?小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 在干什么啊 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小光惹怒了它啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是!那样下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女孩会丧命啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我估计这只魔物本来已发怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾它了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海你好威风!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没受伤吧?光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也和刚才的魔物一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谢加图的关系吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可饶恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点吧 去艾蒂露娜之泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光…风…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海…小海…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等得不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从异世界来\N未成熟的魔法骑士们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在沉默之森不能用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我在这里等你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了报上次的一箭之仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风 小海拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢…竟敢打伤小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看来能用魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但能打赢导师古列夫的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主的魔操士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱尔希欧蕾我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主的…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫先生的弟子!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你是公主的魔操士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何要阻我们去路!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗这里有危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫没告诉你吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那又如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主是支持锡菲罗这里的柱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但公主被神官谢加图捉走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已效忠谢加图大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里等你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是得到谢加图大人的批准
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何要效忠那种家伙!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…我爱他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰枪投射!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光!危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避得真轻松\N但下次就不能那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像那里的小姐一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要你遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢打伤小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风和小海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我在锡菲罗一起并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我宝贵的同伴!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同一种魔法不会再对我有效
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壳圆防除!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:15:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法力量比上次增强了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海被打伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光发怒后的意志力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令魔法增强了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到你能在短时间内
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令魔法力量成长到那地步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.49,0:15:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是!\N那点力量是打不倒我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰流切刀!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃不掉的!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光呢…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她正在和上次那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阴险的大婶战斗!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光自己一个…\N好危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你现在乱动 伤势会恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿…\N你在担心我吗…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我跟你的真正主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个傲慢的魔法使…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虚心学习魔法就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话…我就能救小光了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才…小光救了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要…救小光的魔法!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海 你听到吗?海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我通过莫歌拿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接和你的心说话\N你听到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到 古列夫 你没事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我被变为石头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总算能和你们对话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想救小光 我想要救小光的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:18:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错 你想救小光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了救小光 你想要魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你体内有力量吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一股和以前不同的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 心底好热 话语…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话语…浮现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.44,0:18:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一击!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰枪乱射!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之龙!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!小海…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光…你没事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小海你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海你用魔法…救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了…\N我总觉得不能抛下小光不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像妹妹般可爱…\N拼命地…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫歌拿先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赐我魔法 我想救小海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是古列夫先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你教我魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能救回小海的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:20:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的魔法已经在你体内
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是关怀同伴的心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唤醒你的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.11,0:20:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在锡菲罗这里 意志胜于一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有信念的心在锡菲罗这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会成为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心底有某句话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愈之风!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了!真是太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不痛了吗?伤势没事了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事了 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有信念的心…\N会成为力量!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:21:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢你 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 如果没有小海你的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们或许已经被那大婶杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光也为我们而战 多谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是同伴 是在锡菲罗这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.18,0:21:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有三个的宝贵同伴!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.97,0:21:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们仍然和魔物一样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少有那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有信念的心增加一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世界还开有这么美丽的花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.22,0:22:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把她变回本来的美丽世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在等那一日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起程吧!去艾蒂露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了尽快回复和平!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:10.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:21.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:29.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:37.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,海的颜色逐渐染成红色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,无重力状态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:44.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,想就此被风带走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然以不认输的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:53.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,跳过经常跳不过的栏杆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:01:02.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,但用不完的实力是谁所赐?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:09.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:15.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:20.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心底不褪色的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:25.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,背着阳光透出耀眼光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:38.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,面带最美的笑容用力踏脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:45.59,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,逆风也不可以沮丧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:51.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不输给悲伤的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:58.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄地告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.13,0:23:03.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着广阔海洋前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:10.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 你的瞳孔终有一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:16.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,会在阳光下散发光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:23.46,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不要灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:28.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,把信念化成奔向明日的勇气
